# Surge RULE-SET (explicit DOMAIN / DOMAIN-SUFFIX)
# Policy: US
# Purpose: Route GitHub + Actions + Packages/Registry + Pages + assets/CDNs through Proxy.
#
# Usage (Surge):
#   [Rule]
#   RULE-SET,https://your-domain-or-raw-link/github.list,Proxy
#
# Notes:
# - Converted to explicit rule types for clarity and cross-tool compatibility.
# - DOMAIN      = exact host only
# - DOMAIN-SUFFIX = host + all subdomains

# -----------------------
# Core
# -----------------------
DOMAIN,github.com
DOMAIN,www.github.com
DOMAIN,api.github.com
DOMAIN,uploads.github.com
DOMAIN,codeload.github.com
DOMAIN,raw.github.com
DOMAIN,gist.github.com
DOMAIN,www.gist.github.com

# -----------------------
# Assets / static
# -----------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,githubassets.com
DOMAIN,github.githubassets.com
DOMAIN,collector.githubassets.com

# -----------------------
# User content / blobs / avatars / media
# -----------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,raw.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,user-images.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,avatars.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,avatars0.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,avatars1.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,avatars2.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,avatars3.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,avatars4.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,avatars5.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,avatars6.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,avatars7.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,avatars8.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,avatars9.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,objects.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,media.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,camo.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,cloud.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,favicons.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,private-user-images.githubusercontent.com

# -----------------------
# Pages
# -----------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,github.io
DOMAIN,www.github.io

# -----------------------
# Releases / downloads (common endpoints)
# -----------------------
DOMAIN,github-releases.githubusercontent.com
DOMAIN,github-registry-files.githubusercontent.com

# -----------------------
# App / OAuth related
# -----------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,githubapp.com
DOMAIN,api.githubapp.com

# -----------------------
# Actions (logs/artifacts often land on these GitHub-owned hosts)
# -----------------------
DOMAIN,actions.githubusercontent.com

# -----------------------
# Packages / registries (GitHub Packages)
# -----------------------
DOMAIN,pkg.github.com
DOMAIN,npm.pkg.github.com
DOMAIN,maven.pkg.github.com
DOMAIN,nuget.pkg.github.com
DOMAIN,rubygems.pkg.github.com
DOMAIN,docker.pkg.github.com
DOMAIN,container.pkg.github.com

# -----------------------
# Status (optional but useful when troubleshooting)
# -----------------------
DOMAIN,githubstatus.com
DOMAIN,www.githubstatus.com
DOMAIN,githubcopilot.com